        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>No Action Cost</strong> - Magical​</p><p>Your &amp;reference[illusoryimages]{illusory image} spells of 1st level or higher grant you a flying speed of 10 ft. when:​</p><ul><li><p>You cast an illusory image spell on yourself, such as with <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.mcpWUlgl737AIttd]{Disguise Self}</em>.</p></li><li><p>You are within the area of an illusory image spell you cast, such as <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.4aj73yzrHMc6N16Y]{Silent Image}</em>.</p></li></ul><p>If your spell ends or you are no longer within the area of your image, you immediately lose the fly speed and fall.</p><p> </p><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.bVLJ0ANP3MIhT5np]{Shadow Clone}</em> allows your clone to fly this way but not yourself.</p>",
